title: PrimaryEntityTypes
description: Defines the data needed for presenting entity types in the UI

entityName.description: Corresponds to the value of info.title in the model

entityTypeId.description: Unique identifier for an entity type that combines the entity name, base URI, and version number

latestJobId.description: If at least one instance of this type has been processed by a job, then this will contain the ID of the most recent such job.

latestJobDateTime.description: If latestJobId is populated, then this will contain the dateTime of the most entity instance of this type most recently processed.
